# Filmxy Multi Stremio Addon (4K + Subtitles)

Aggregates streams from **Filmxy.vip**, **Streamx.sh**, **Cinevo.site**, and **Fluxtv.qzz.io**.

## Features
- Up to **4K** resolution (when available)
- Integrated subtitle support
- Fast parallel scraping
- Quality priority sorting

## Installation

1. Deploy on Render / Railway / Fly.io / VPS
2. In Stremio go to **Addons → Install from URL**
3. Paste: `https://your-deployed-url/manifest.json`

## Local Testing
```bash
npm install
node index.js
